title: BlackBerry: Z10 Return Claims Are `False'
description:
April 12 (Bloomberg) -- BlackBerry will ask securities regulators to investigate a report that its new phones have high return rates, arguing that the "false" information may have been released in a deliberate attempt to manipulate its stock price. Jon Erlichman reports on Bloomberg Television's "Bloomberg West." (Source: Bloomberg)
